      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I'm working on a new global campaign for a high-end luxury watch brand. We need to nail the target demographic for the creative assets. Can you help me outline a detailed persona for our \"ideal consumer\"? I need to know their lifestyle, where they travel, their aesthetic, and also their ethnic/cultural background so we can make sure the casting and settings feel authentic to the brand's prestige.",
